//pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 181}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "超 7 成年轻人存款不足 10 万引发热议，如何看待这一现象，可能由哪些原因导致？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，红星资本局对生活在一线与二线城市年龄在 20～30 岁之间的年轻人，进行了一次关于「存钱与消费」的线上问卷调查。在 2035 份有效问卷中，存款在 10 万以下的年轻人占比超 7 成。大部分年轻人的存款，主要集中在 3 万元以下以及 3～10 万元这两个存款区间。存款超过 50 万的年轻人，占比不超过 2%；而存款超百万的人，更是少之又少；超 2000 名受访者中，存款过百万的仅有个位数。从这些受访者的月收入状况来看，接近 7 成的年轻人表示自己的月收入在 1 万元以下。最后，当被问到要存多少钱才能让自己「退休」时，有超 5 成的受访者表示，自己若有 50-200 万的存款，就会考虑「退休」。#超 7 成年轻人存款不足 10 万#上热搜 评论区炸了 _ 生活 _ 消费 _ 一线"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f4b35af4be5d1e8956241374c481f18d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "113 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/610222653"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ir6Kmktq4yspjEAMaCDk3ODg1Nzc3ILXnjaUGMAA4lAJACHIJNjEwMjIyNjUzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1689066320.952673", "card_id": "Q_609861877", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《海贼王》漫画第 1087 话情报？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-878ce166e294f44765f37e4007f4ff0a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "107 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/609861877"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ir6Kmktq4yspjEAMaCDk3ODA1NDcwINm7gaUGMAA4HkAJcgk2MDk4NjE4Nzd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1689066320.953104", "card_id": "Q_611304371", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}